snippet.title: Prepare your weapons and start your engines: Super Hydorah arrives!
snippet.description:
Stand ready for the battle that will decide the future of the universe!

Super Hydorah is a side scroller non-linear SHMUP which gives the player a challenging experience with the best from the greatest classics of the genre: straightforward action, old school visuals and a wide array of content with unique space settings.

Now available on Xbox One & Steam:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/628800/Super_Hydorah/

https://www.microsoft.com/es-es/store/p/super-hydorah/bwd1jltpbd16
